# UI Components and Pages

## Core Components

Key reusable components in [src/components/](mdc:src/components):
- [src/components/Navbar.tsx](mdc:src/components/Navbar.tsx) - Navigation bar component
- [src/components/DeviceStatus.tsx](mdc:src/components/DeviceStatus.tsx) - ESP32 device connection status
- [src/components/FileBrowser.tsx](mdc:src/components/FileBrowser.tsx) - Component for browsing files
- [src/components/StorageFileBrowser.tsx](mdc:src/components/StorageFileBrowser.tsx) - Component for browsing device storage
- [src/components/FileUploader.tsx](mdc:src/components/FileUploader.tsx) - File upload component
- [src/components/ZXSpectrum.tsx](mdc:src/components/ZXSpectrum.tsx) - ZX Spectrum emulator component

## Pages

The application routes in [src/pages/](mdc:src/pages):
- [src/pages/Home.tsx](mdc:src/pages/Home.tsx) - Main landing page
- [src/pages/FileBrowser.tsx](mdc:src/pages/FileBrowser.tsx) - File browser page
- [src/pages/Games.tsx](mdc:src/pages/Games.tsx) - Games listing page
- [src/pages/GameDetail.tsx](mdc:src/pages/GameDetail.tsx) - Game details page
- [src/pages/Emulator.tsx](mdc:src/pages/Emulator.tsx) - Emulator page
- [src/pages/Firmware.tsx](mdc:src/pages/Firmware.tsx) - Firmware management
- [src/pages/Docs.tsx](mdc:src/pages/Docs.tsx) - Documentation page
- Utility pages for file conversions (Tap, Scr, Binary, etc.)
